@startuml CourseManagement
left to right direction

actor "Instructor" as instructor
actor "Administrator" as admin
actor "Student" as student
actor "System (Scout)" as scout_system

rectangle "Course Management System" {
  usecase "Create Course" as UC0201
  usecase "Validate Metadata" as validate_metadata
  usecase "Edit Course Content" as UC0202
  usecase "Index Content" as index_content
  usecase "Publish Course" as UC0203
  usecase "Validate Content" as validate_content
  usecase "Manage Categories" as UC0204
  usecase "Update Hierarchy" as update_hierarchy
  usecase "View Published Courses" as view_courses
}

' Actor Associations
instructor --> UC0201 : **Association**
instructor --> UC0202 : **Association**
instructor --> UC0203 : **Association**
admin --> UC0204 : **Association**
student --> view_courses : **Association**
scout_system --> index_content : **Association**

' Use Case Relationships
UC0201 ..> validate_metadata : **<<include>>**
UC0202 ..> index_content : **<<include>>**
UC0203 ..> validate_content : **<<extend>>**
UC0204 ..> update_hierarchy : **<<include>>**

@enduml